                                <rect key="frame" x="16" y="302.33333333333331" width="361" height="218.33333333333331"/>
                                <string key="text">1. Each level introduces a new set of cards for you to complete.
2. Difficulty increases slowly as you move forward.
3. Finish the current level to unlock the next one.
4. Take your time, you can replay any level anytime.
5. After completing each level, you can see the time taken to finish.</string>
                                <fontDescription key="fontDescription" style="UICTFontTextStyleBody"/>
